  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/72e7dfe52e4ac66df8dc744092ee0516.poster.avif?t=1670358312\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/72e7dfe52e4ac66df8dc744092ee0516.webm?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/72e7dfe52e4ac66df8dc744092ee0516.mp4?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>♦ One after another, each step is important.<br><br>♦ The goal is to find a way to solve the puzzle by reaching the light, in this process you need to explore the possibilities and develop your skills to discover the rules.<br><br>♦ You guide your steps in four directions, up, down, left and right.<br>♦ CONTROLS: WASD or Arrow Keys (grid based movement)<br><br>♦ 40 unique handcrafted levels. ( ~1 hour gameplay)<br>♦ No tutorials.<br><br>♦ On your journey you will find several elements that will help or hinder you, such as portals, enemies, doors, collectibles, among other things you will discover.<br><br>♦ Test your skills, and see if you can find the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/76f3e89cd00635fba9ce1ef30bf0ad1b.poster.avif?t=1670358312\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/76f3e89cd00635fba9ce1ef30bf0ad1b.webm?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/76f3e89cd00635fba9ce1ef30bf0ad1b.mp4?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/41131914b50d0d54b87d343f46e21001.poster.avif?t=1670358312\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/41131914b50d0d54b87d343f46e21001.webm?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/41131914b50d0d54b87d343f46e21001.mp4?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/a8791c8bf13a81f3a9335d0246d00c04.poster.avif?t=1670358312\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/a8791c8bf13a81f3a9335d0246d00c04.webm?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/a8791c8bf13a81f3a9335d0246d00c04.mp4?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/03df1b967ea299e164d64c3a35a42cf3.poster.avif?t=1670358312\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/03df1b967ea299e164d64c3a35a42cf3.webm?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062750/extras/03df1b967ea299e164d64c3a35a42cf3.mp4?t=1670358312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
